Name: Lost Kittens: Maze Garden
About the game: Maze Garden is a cute and relaxing game, but one that can get you tense sometimes, where your goal will be to find the kittens and your main challenge will be not to get lost in a variety of 50 different mazes . And be careful not to fall into the water or get burned on the way, as you'll have to restart the level. The mazes were designed one-by-one to provide progressive difficulty, but some are intended to be very difficult, are you up to the challenge? More than one character available to choose from. Collect coins to unlock new abilities and skins 50 hand-crafted levels with increasing complexity and 50 achievements to be collected; 2 theme options, Normal and Halloween, which you can choose to play in all stages. With themed decor and soundtrack. Beautiful backgrounds in a cartoonish and cute pixel art style; Original soundtrack created exclusively for the game;
